1) How to start a server
   > start server 
   > Open Cmd and navigate to bin 
   > Go inside the folder  c:\program file\mongoDb\5.5\server\bin
   > Mongo 
   (start server on port 27017)
   > Do not close this cnd if using mongoDb
   (Client ) ** Only require to test queries
   -> Open cnd and navigate to bin
   > Mongo

